{"tid":566563,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】杜奧巴加盟法甲球隊！","createTime":"2018-02-20T05:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T14:14:01.000Z","uid":4661,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e48c98fc16d9bddac76662e6f8809af552d945bd","tid":566563,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T05:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2018/02/20/f/f19e0b77138d6df8872f49db4e2b9812.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2Ff%2Ff19e0b77138d6df8872f49db4e2b9812.jpg&h=4dc157a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突發？！杜奧巴加盟法甲球隊？大家別緊張，現在講緊的是杜奧巴的仔仔艾薩克杜奧巴。<br />\n法甲球隊甘岡宣佈簽入17歲的艾薩克杜奧巴，而這位小球員正式前車路士傳球杜奧巴的兒子，他將會在U19賽事中率先上陣。<br />\n17歲的艾薩克杜奧巴曾經都在車路士受訓，之後就轉加盟到勒芒比賽，上陣50場就攻入24球。隨後小杜奧巴以80,000英鎊轉會到法甲法甲球隊甘岡，而當年仍是16歲的杜奧巴都是效力緊同一支球隊。不知道17歲的仔仔是否想跟隨父親的步伐，立志要成為球壇的傳奇之一呢？<br />\n甘岡在 Twitter 上都正式官宣艾薩克杜奧巴的加盟消息，父親杜奧巴都在 Instagram 表示︰「為艾薩克杜奧巴感到自豪。」"},{"pid":"617796a1b03acefe9e698b94e8cf06fdbad9280d","tid":566563,"uid":2757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T05:18:59.000Z","msg":"北京電視機"},{"pid":"f9106b66ce20e24320c52ea8bdaca68d2de0e20f","tid":566563,"uid":1914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T05:21:42.000Z","msg":"條jer鏟唔鏟到草先"},{"pid":"0c3c861f6353a87c1491073e95dc2bea91042cbe","tid":566563,"uid":269,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"餅印咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd46affcfb6bb4faad1c55e0cc43513f8628079e","tid":566563,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"回家吧巴哥 咩盧卡古 達仔 銀河第一都係假<br />\n巴哥個仔返來頂巴哥個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 